<SYNC START=2729636><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2729781><P Class=KRCC>
여자 꿈이겠지
<SYNC START=2734514><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC START=2737789><P Class=KRCC>
